name: Heritage Home in coolest neighborhood in Vancouver
description:
Gorgeous Heritage Home in Mount Pleasant is located across from a park, in very close walking distance to cool Main Street, Downtown, VGH, the Canada Line and the 99! This completely furnished home has three bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, 2 living rooms, a piano, sit in kitchen with beautiful appliances, and a dining room. There are bikes to use as well.

The space
There is everything you need from towels, sheets, pillows, and a washer and dryer on the 2nd floor of the home. There are two full baths with bathtubs and 1 bedroom has an en suite 1/2 bathroom. There is a wrap around porch that leads from the kitchen. In the backyard is a patio as well and a place for kids to run around. There is room for a car in my driveway. There are several bikes and helmets for your use.
